data.description: Seller offering $5,000 towards buyers closing costs with accepted offer! If you missed this home the first time around now is your chance to secure this one-of-a-kind property! Beautiful 3-bed 2.5 bath plus study home boasts over 2000 sf and is located on a quiet no through traffic street! Sit on the front porch with your morning coffee and enjoy the absolutely stunning views of the Wichita Mountains. Cache School District and great location to Fort Sill military base. NO HOA!!! This home is situated on a private lot that boasts over 1-acre with a 20 x 30 insulated shop with its own electric, a playhouse, an inground concrete pool and a fully fenced area around the pool. This amazing brand new inground custom concrete pool is 16x32 with a gradual slope to a 6’ deep end. The Baja shelf with water jet feature and umbrella is perfect for those hot Oklahoma Summers. At night flip on the Jandy Pro Series lighting with 14 different colors! There are umbrella hole inserts in 4 areas around the deck for shade. As you enter the home you will fall in love with the open floorplan, beautiful wood burning floor to ceiling stone masonry fireplace with wood mantle. This home has stunning natural lighting and features gorgeous contemporary paint colors that greet you upon entry with tall ceilings. There is an office/bonus room perfect for teleworking or a kid's playroom directly off of the front door. The kitchen was meticulously designed with beautiful cabinetry, granite countertops, matching backsplash, stainless-steel appliances and a large walk-in pantry. The oversized primary bedroom comes with a beautiful ensuite equipped with a spacious walk-in closet with built-ins. The oversized secondary bedrooms both have walk-in closets. New carpet throughout all bedrooms! This meticulously designed home also features an Oxy-4 ion whole home air purification system and an above ground safe room! Zero turn mower, pool equipment, new pool vacuum, lawn tools to stay with acceptable offer.
